  div.col-md-4
    h2 Find a Cause
    p Search through causes both national and local to find people making change you believe in.
  div.col-md-4
    h2 Give Support
    p Support a cause by pledging twenty-five cents a month. Think twenty-five cents isn't enough? Of course not! Tell your friends about my-two-cents and build support for causes you believe in.
  div.col-md-4
