    p Are you an organization doing charitable work? Is your company or non-profit organization trying to change the world for the better? Register with my-two-cents to find supporters now.
div.row
  div.col-md-4
    h3 Member login
    div.form-group
      input.form-control(ng-model='login.username' placeholder='Username')
    div.form-group
      input.form-control(type='password' ng-model='login.password' placeholder='Password')
    div.form-group
      select.form-control(name='type' ng-model='login.type')
        option(value='user') User
        option(value='organization') Organization
    button(class='btn btn-default', ng-click='login()') Login
  div.col-md-4
    h3 Register
    div.form-group
      input.form-control(ng-model='reg.username' placeholder='Username')
    div.form-group
      input.form-control(type='password' ng-model='reg.password' placeholder='Password')
    div.form-group
      select.form-control(name='type' ng-model='reg.type')
        option(value='user') User
        option(value='organization') Organization
    button(class='btn btn-default', ng-click='register()') Register
  div.col-md-4
    h3 More Information:
